# Customer Churn Prediction - MLOps Pipeline

## Project Overview

This project implements a complete MLOps pipeline for predicting customer churn using the IBM Telco Customer Churn dataset.

The pipeline automates the entire machine learning workflow, including:

- Data loading
- Data preprocessing
- Feature engineering
- Model training
- Model evaluation
- Experiment tracking with MLflow

This project was developed as part of the Machine Learning course.

---

## Dataset

IBM Telco Customer Churn Dataset

Dataset versions:

- v1 : Raw dataset (.xlsx)
- v2 : Cleaned dataset (.csv)
- v3 : Feature engineered dataset (.csv)

